    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RAkELd, SCC

    public class NSR
extends PS
implements MultiTargetClassifier
    NSR.java - The Nearest Set Relpacement (NSR) method. A multi-target version of PS: The nearest sets are used to replace outliers, rather than subsets (as in PS). Important Note: currently can only handle 10 values (or fewer) per target variable.
    Version:
    Jan 2013
    Author:
    Jesse Read
    See Also:
    PS, Serialized Form
